result.name: Shake Shack Pacific Place

reviews.text: Great milk shakes, reasonable food. Comfortable environment with good service. Good place to hang out with friends. While still new, hopefully the food (while still good) will get to the level of the US and UK branches. Waiting time for food/drinks can be a slightly long.
Really yummy food and good design in the restaurant. For a fast food restaurant it's a bit expensive. Really crowded at times.

Great food, great service, lovely staff always welcoming and greeting others as they come in or pick up their order. 

Seating is really comfy and spacious. Great vibe and atmosphere in all.

They have a machine that assists with hand washing as well. Great location as well, located near the cinema.
No queue here! Awesome shack burger. A lil pricey though. We paid ~200hkd for two set meals.

The food are good, but a bit over priced.
Prime location at Pacific place. 

With a seasoning bar and a machine for washing hands, very considerate. Also water fountain and paper cup. Good that this place still provides straw and spoon for shake.

Staff are international and polite, very friendly. 

There are seating area and about 10 spots for those stand and eat.

reviews.text: God burger! Spiste både shack burger(HK$ 50) og smoke burger (tror det var HK$ 62). Min forlover likte smoke, mens jeg likte shack best, så alt etter smak. Burgeren var god, men ikke noe som skilte seg særlig ut i fra andre plasser. Pommes-frites med ost var derimot kjempe god. Veldig hyggelige damer som jobbet der. Lemonade-drikke var kjempe god, mens isteen var bare overpriset.

Great milk shakes, reasonable food. Comfortable environment with good service. Good place to hang out with friends. While still new, hopefully the food (while still good) will get to the level of the US and UK branches. Waiting time for food/drinks can be a slightly long.
Donne envie de déguster de la nourriture rapide même aux adeptes de mets plus raffinés. Service très rapide. Climatisation bien réglée.
